data.description: Original Owners On This Nicely Cared For Ranch In A Great Neighborhood Tucked Away North Off Cooper Foster That's Very Walkable! Walking Into The Foyer With The 1st Bedroom Just Inside The Foyer Area & Full Shared Bath Opening Up To A Bright Open Floor Plan Featuring The Great Room W/kitchen, Dining Area & Family Room With Nice Gas Fireplace And Plenty Of Windows Letting In Natural Light. The Back Of The House Faces South So There's Plenty Of Light Throughout The Day & Early Evening. The Opposite Side Of The House Has The Master Suite With New Carpet, En-suite Bathroom & Walk In Closet. The Main Floor Laundry Is There Also Leading To The Nice 2 Car Garage. The Stairway Takes You To The Full Dry Unfinished Basement Waiting For Your Ideas To Finish Along With Mechanicals. This Is Easy Living With A Minimal Hoa That Takes Care Of Your Grass, Landscape & Snow Removal. Move Into The Neighborhood & Relax.
